<li><a href="http://www.siue.edu/artsandsciences/philosophy/weilsociety/colloquy.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.siue.edu/artsandsciences/philosophy/weilsociety/colloquy.shtml" rel="nofollow">American Weil Society and 2009 Colloquy</a> - Website for 2009 Colloquy at Southern Illinois University Edwardsville</li>
<li><a href="http://members.aol.com/geojade/" class="external text" title="http://members.aol.com/geojade/" rel="nofollow">Simone Weil's Home Page</a> - An unofficial page dedicated to Simone Weil</li>
<li><a href="http://www.rivertext.com/weil.html" class="external text" title="http://www.rivertext.com/weil.html" rel="nofollow">Welcome to the Simone Weil home page NEWS</a> at www.rivertext.com - An unofficial page dedicated to Simone Weil</li>
<li><a href="http://www.chemins-cathares.eu/010301_simone_weil.php" class="external text" title="http://www.chemins-cathares.eu/010301_simone_weil.php" rel="nofollow">Letter of Simone Weil to Déodat Roché</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/13783" class="external text" title="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/13783" rel="nofollow">Simone Weil</a>, an article in <a href="/wiki/The_New_York_Review_of_Books" title="The New York Review of Books">The New York Review of Books</a> by <a href="/wiki/Susan_Sontag" title="Susan Sontag">Susan Sontag</a>.</li>
<li>Center for Global Justice, <a href="http://www.globaljusticecenter.org/papers2005/presbey_eng.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.globaljusticecenter.org/papers2005/presbey_eng.htm" rel="nofollow">Simone Weil on Labor</a></li>
<li><a href="http://simoneweil.net/home.htm" class="external text" title="http://simoneweil.net/home.htm" rel="nofollow">simoneweil.net</a> biographical notes, photos &amp; bilingual quotes that illustrate key concepts, including force, necessity, attention and "le malheur"</li>
<li><a href="http://www.vitalpoetics.com/literature-and-hope-sartres-commitment-camus-rebellion-and-weils-metaxu" class="external text" title="http://www.vitalpoetics.com/literature-and-hope-sartres-commitment-camus-rebellion-and-weils-metaxu" rel="nofollow">"Metaxu"</a> - An article about Simone Weil's 'metaxu.'</li>
<li><a href="http://wikilivres.info/wiki/Simone_Weil" class="extiw" title="wikilivres:Simone Weil">Works by Simone Weil</a> (public domain in Canada)</li>
</ul>


